{
  "stem": "19596.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 304.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wherever they had to go-- to Germany to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of them slept with them because they thought being in favor with them, they would let them go, which is--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, we know that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no-- I-- I wasn't the type of a peeping Tom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we knew they were on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They get special foods and they had more than anybody else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food was plenty of food, because-- plenty of food because the Jews were bringing food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you know our people, wherever they go, they're-- just in case, they bring a few tins and the food with them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the-- the-- the-- what you call it, the kitchen was full with food from people who came from [? home ?] not from jails, and brought food over there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About a week, 10 days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes loading a truck or something like that with food, but they wanted a few volunteers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking about February 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And transports were going every week to work to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We supposed to work in factories and industry, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, you know, together with the wives and the children, and they give you accommodation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the wife is working in a factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the-- and that's what all we knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know anything else-- somewhere in Germany, somewhere maybe in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they were worried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They want to go home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, they were not worried to such an extent [? and ?] you mean they would be exterminated.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody thought about that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There in Belgium there was a concentration camp called Breendonk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was a concentration camp for people who were punished of doing something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They put us on transport.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
